---
/**
 * 3-act mechanism teaser for the homepage.
 * ATTEMPT → RESET → REPEAT. RESET carries the emphasis.
 * The schematic is the hero: external forces fail, the spring returns the pin,
 * the loop closes.
 */
---

<section class="section section-dark border-t border-white/5">
  <div class="container-page">
    <header class="max-w-2xl reveal">
      <p class="kicker">The mechanism</p>
      <h2 class="h2-section mt-3">It only opens one way. Every other way, it resets.</h2>
    </header>

    <div
      class="mt-14 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_1.4fr_1fr] border-y border-brand-bone/10"
    >
      <!-- ACT I — ATTEMPT -->
      <article
        class="reveal relative py-10 px-6 md:px-8 border-b md:border-b-0 md:border-r border-brand-bone/10"
      >
        <p class="font-mono text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-brand-bone-muted">
          ACT I &middot; ATTEMPT
        </p>

        <div class="mt-6 flex items-center justify-center min-h-[190px] text-brand-bone">
          <svg
            viewBox="0 0 200 120"
            class="w-full max-w-[260px] h-auto"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="1.25"
            stroke-linecap="square"
            stroke-linejoin="miter"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <rect x="10" y="35" width="100" height="50" />
            <rect x="115" y="48" width="55" height="24" />
            <rect x="175" y="35" width="20" height="50" />
            <polyline points="20,60 30,55 40,65 50,55 60,65 70,55 80,65 90,55 100,65" stroke-width="1" />
            <circle cx="22" cy="60" r="2.5" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" />

            <!-- Stronger force vectors -->
            <line x1="142" y1="12" x2="142" y2="44" stroke-width="1.5" />
            <polyline points="137,38 142,46 147,38" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" />

            <line x1="142" y1="108" x2="142" y2="76" stroke-width="1.5" />
            <polyline points="137,82 142,74 147,82" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" />

            <line x1="190" y1="100" x2="166" y2="76" stroke-width="1.5" />
            <polyline points="171,75 165,75 167,82" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" />
          </svg>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-6 text-[15px] text-brand-white/80 leading-relaxed">
          Push, paw, nudge, vibrate. The bolt holds.
        </p>
      </article>

      <!-- ACT II — RESET (emphasis) -->
      <article
        class="reveal relative py-12 px-6 md:px-10 border-b md:border-b-0 md:border-r border-brand-bone/10 bg-brand-green/[0.08] ring-1 ring-inset ring-brand-green/20"
      >
        <p class="font-mono text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-brand-green">
          ACT II &middot; RESET
        </p>

        <div class="mt-6 flex items-center justify-center min-h-[220px] text-brand-bone">
          <svg
            viewBox="0 0 200 120"
            class="w-full max-w-[360px] h-auto"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="1.25"
            stroke-linecap="square"
            stroke-linejoin="miter"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <rect x="10" y="35" width="100" height="50" />
            <rect x="115" y="48" width="55" height="24" />
            <rect x="175" y="35" width="20" height="50" />

            <g class="text-brand-green">
              <polyline
                points="20,60 30,55 40,65 50,55 60,65 70,55 80,65 90,55 100,65"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="1.5"
              />
              <circle cx="58" cy="60" r="3" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" />
              <path
                d="M 58 48 Q 40 25 22 48"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                fill="none"
              />
              <polyline
                points="18,44 22,50 26,44"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                fill="none"
              />
            </g>
          </svg>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-6 text-base text-brand-white leading-relaxed">
          Hand off, intent off. The spring returns the pin to locked. Automatic. Every time.
        </p>
      </article>

      <!-- ACT III — REPEAT -->
      <article class="reveal relative py-10 px-6 md:px-8">
        <p class="font-mono text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-brand-bone-muted">
          ACT III &middot; REPEAT
        </p>

        <div class="mt-6 flex items-center justify-center min-h-[190px] text-brand-bone">
          <svg
            viewBox="0 0 200 120"
            class="w-full max-w-[260px] h-auto"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="1.25"
            stroke-linecap="square"
            stroke-linejoin="miter"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <rect x="10" y="35" width="100" height="50" />
            <rect x="115" y="48" width="55" height="24" />
            <rect x="175" y="35" width="20" height="50" />
            <polyline points="20,60 30,55 40,65 50,55 60,65 70,55 80,65 90,55 100,65" stroke-width="1" />
            <circle cx="22" cy="60" r="2.5" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" />

            <line x1="142" y1="12" x2="142" y2="44" stroke-width="1.5" />
            <polyline points="137,38 142,46 147,38" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" />

            <line x1="142" y1="108" x2="142" y2="76" stroke-width="1.5" />
            <polyline points="137,82 142,74 147,82" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" />

            <line x1="190" y1="100" x2="166" y2="76" stroke-width="1.5" />
            <polyline points="171,75 165,75 167,82" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" />

            <!-- Cycle indicator: mono tag + larger glyph -->
            <g class="text-brand-bone-muted" opacity="0.75">
              <text x="155" y="14" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="7" font-weight="600" fill="currentColor" letter-spacing="0.5">ATTEMPT 02</text>
              <g transform="translate(184, 22)" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.15" fill="none">
                <path d="M 0 6 a 6 6 0 1 1 -2 4.5" />
                <polyline points="-4,12 -2,4.5 4.5,7" />
              </g>
            </g>
          </svg>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-6 text-[15px] text-brand-white/80 leading-relaxed">
          Try again. Same outcome. Patented in seven markets.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 reveal">
      <a href="/how-it-works" class="btn btn-ghost">
        See the five-step sequence <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
